At this time, we cannot ship this item to Alaska, Hawaii, Guam, Puerto Rico, any international locations, P.O. Boxes, or military addresses (APO/FPO). You thrive in the sweltering heat. To you, there's nothing better than feeling the sun's warm embrace after leaving an air-conditioned room. Celebrate the season the right way with this sunny nail polish collection from Essie! ; This collection features maritime pastels in six soothing shades inspired by summer's hottest looks. Color names and descriptions (please note, some might be out of stock): Full Steam Ahead is a medium-toned lilac with a pearlescent purple punch. Girls Are Out is a soft fuchsia peony infused with subtle sparkle. Naughty Nautical is a softly shimmering, brilliant blue-green teal marine. Rock the Boat is a shimmering light French blue with a hint of periwinkle. Sunday Funday is a beautiful, bright tangerine coral with soft shimmer. The More the Merrier is a juicy lime green.
